data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_13","content":"8:  <meta name=\"review-provenance\" content=\"ai-reference-placeholder; replace with real Google or customer reviews before live\" />\n264:      \"address\": {\n267:        \"addressLocality\": \"Brisbane\",\n268:        \"addressRegion\": \"QLD\",\n269:        \"addressCountry\": \"AU\"\n298:          <p class=\"lead\">RidgeLine Roof Co. helps homeowners and property managers plan roof repairs, restorations, gutter repairs and inspections with straight answers before the work starts.</p>\n332:          <p class=\"lead\">Use the form for a repair, restoration or inspection request. The page avoids claims that need verification and focuses on the work customers commonly need priced.</p>\n356:            <p>Gutter repairs, roof condition checks and pre-work inspections for owners who need a practical next step, not guesswork.</p>\n500:          <p class=\"meta\" style=\"margin: 16px 0 0;\">This concept form is ready to connect to the business enquiry system before publishing.</p>\n","isError":false}

