ntact-footer\">\n469:            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"tel:0400000000\">Call now</a>\n506:  <footer class=\"pagefoot\" data-od-id=\"footer\">\n509:      <span class=\"meta\">Brisbane and Gold Coast · <a href=\"tel:0400000000\">0400 000 000</a> · <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Brisbane+roofing+contractor\">Directions placeholder</a></span>\n","isError":false}

